MACHINE.PGenPu.comment: Active power at terminal in p.u (base SnRef) (generator convention)

MACHINE.QGenPu.comment: Reactive power at terminal in p.u (base SnRef) (generator convention)

MACHINE.UPu.comment: Voltage amplitude at terminal in p.u (base UNom)

MACHINE.pStatus.comment: Status of the power / frequency regulation function

MACHINE.AlphaPu.comment: Frequency sensitivity in p.u (base SnRef, OmegaNom)

MACHINE.PMaxPu.comment: Maximum active power in p.u (base SnRef)

MACHINE.PMinPu.comment: Minimum active power in p.u (base SnRef)

MACHINE.QGen0Pu.comment: Start value of reactive power at terminal in p.u (base SnRef) (generator convention)

MACHINE.QMaxPu.comment: Maximum reactive power in p.u (base SnRef)

MACHINE.QMinPu.comment: Minimum reactive power in p.u (base SnRef)

MACHINE.U0Pu.comment: Start value of voltage at terminal amplitude in p.u (base UNom)

MACHINE.NbSwitchOffSignals.comment: Number of switch-off signals to take into account in inputs

equation: MACHINE.UPu < -0.0001 + MACHINE.UMaxPu and $PRE.MACHINE.qStatus == Dynawo.Electrical.Machines.GeneratorPQ.QStatus.absorptionMax or MACHINE.UPu > 0.0001 + MACHINE.UMinPu and $PRE.MACHINE.qStatus == Dynawo.Electrical.Machines.GeneratorPQ.QStatus.generationMax
MACHINE.switchOffSignal1.value or MACHINE.switchOffSignal2.value or MACHINE.switchOffSignal3.value and $PRE.MACHINE.running.value
if MACHINE.running.value then MACHINE.PGen0Pu + MACHINE.AlphaPu * (1.0 - MACHINE.omegaRefPu.value) else 0.0

if MACHINE.running.value then if MACHINE.pStatus == Dynawo.Electrical.Machines.GeneratorPQ.PStatus.limitPMax then MACHINE.PMaxPu else if MACHINE.pStatus == Dynawo.Electrical.Machines.GeneratorPQ.PStatus.limitPMin then MACHINE.PMinPu else MACHINE.PGenRawPu else 0.0

if MACHINE.running.value then if $PRE.MACHINE.qStatus == Dynawo.Electrical.Machines.GeneratorPQ.QStatus.absorptionMax then MACHINE.QMaxPu else if $PRE.MACHINE.qStatus == Dynawo.Electrical.Machines.GeneratorPQ.QStatus.generationMax then MACHINE.QMinPu else MACHINE.QGen0Pu else 0.0
MACHINE.switchOffSignal1.value or MACHINE.switchOffSignal2.value or MACHINE.switchOffSignal3.value and pre(MACHINE.running.value)
if MACHINE.running.value then MACHINE.PGen0Pu + MACHINE.AlphaPu * (1.0 - MACHINE.omegaRefPu.value) else 0.0

if MACHINE.running.value then if MACHINE.pStatus == Dynawo.Electrical.Machines.GeneratorPQ.PStatus.limitPMax then MACHINE.PMaxPu else if MACHINE.pStatus == Dynawo.Electrical.Machines.GeneratorPQ.PStatus.limitPMin then MACHINE.PMinPu else MACHINE.PGenRawPu else 0.0

MACHINE.UPu < -0.0001 + MACHINE.UMaxPu and pre(MACHINE.qStatus) == Dynawo.Electrical.Machines.GeneratorPQ.QStatus.absorptionMax or MACHINE.UPu > 0.0001 + MACHINE.UMinPu and pre(MACHINE.qStatus) == Dynawo.Electrical.Machines.GeneratorPQ.QStatus.generationMax

if MACHINE.running.value then if pre(MACHINE.qStatus) == Dynawo.Electrical.Machines.GeneratorPQ.QStatus.absorptionMax then MACHINE.QMaxPu else if pre(MACHINE.qStatus) == Dynawo.Electrical.Machines.GeneratorPQ.QStatus.generationMax then MACHINE.QMinPu else MACHINE.QGen0Pu else 0.0

assert(MACHINE.NbSwitchOffSignals >= 1 and MACHINE.NbSwitchOffSignals <= 3, "Variable MACHINE.NbSwitchOffSignals out of [min, max] interval: MACHINE.NbSwitchOffSignals >= 1 and MACHINE.NbSwitchOffSignals <= 3 has value: " + String(MACHINE.NbSwitchOffSignals, "d"));

assert(MACHINE.State0 >= Dynawo.Electrical.Constants.state.OPEN and MACHINE.State0 <= Dynawo.Electrical.Constants.state.UNDEFINED, "Variable MACHINE.State0 out of [min, max] interval: MACHINE.State0 >= Dynawo.Electrical.Constants.state.OPEN and MACHINE.State0 <= Dynawo.Electrical.Constants.state.UNDEFINED has value: " + String(MACHINE.State0, "d"));

assert(MACHINE.state >= Dynawo.Electrical.Constants.state$MACHINE$state.OPEN and MACHINE.state <= Dynawo.Electrical.Constants.state$MACHINE$state.UNDEFINED, "Variable MACHINE.state out of [min, max] interval: MACHINE.state >= Dynawo.Electrical.Constants.state$MACHINE$state.OPEN and MACHINE.state <= Dynawo.Electrical.Constants.state$MACHINE$state.UNDEFINED has value: " + String(MACHINE.state, "d"));

assert(MACHINE.pStatus >= Dynawo.Electrical.Machines.GeneratorPQ.PStatus$MACHINE$pStatus.standard and MACHINE.pStatus <= Dynawo.Electrical.Machines.GeneratorPQ.PStatus$MACHINE$pStatus.limitPMax, "Variable MACHINE.pStatus out of [min, max] interval: MACHINE.pStatus >= Dynawo.Electrical.Machines.GeneratorPQ.PStatus$MACHINE$pStatus.standard and MACHINE.pStatus <= Dynawo.Electrical.Machines.GeneratorPQ.PStatus$MACHINE$pStatus.limitPMax has value: " + String(MACHINE.pStatus, "d"));

assert(MACHINE.qStatus >= Dynawo.Electrical.Machines.GeneratorPQ.QStatus$MACHINE$qStatus.standard and MACHINE.qStatus <= Dynawo.Electrical.Machines.GeneratorPQ.QStatus$MACHINE$qStatus.generationMax, "Variable MACHINE.qStatus out of [min, max] interval: MACHINE.qStatus >= Dynawo.Electrical.Machines.GeneratorPQ.QStatus$MACHINE$qStatus.standard and MACHINE.qStatus <= Dynawo.Electrical.Machines.GeneratorPQ.QStatus$MACHINE$qStatus.generationMax has value: " + String(MACHINE.qStatus, "d"));
